      "id": "n3",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 2,
      "text": "The official telc Deutsch A2 Lesen subtest is completed inside the shared 50-minute Lesen und Schreiben block. It has 15 items across three Teile and focuses on practical written texts from everyday life."
    },
    {
      "id": "n4",
      "type": "heading",
      "order": 3,
      "level": 4,
      "text": "Teil 1: Aufgaben und Information (Tasks and Information)"
    },
    {
      "id": "n5",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 4,
      "text": "• Read the situations and one information text"
    },
    {
      "id": "n6",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 5,
      "text": "• Choose the correct answer: a, b, or c"
    },
    {
      "id": "n7",
      "type": "heading",
      "order": 6,
      "level": 4,
      "text": "Teil 2: Text und Aussagen (Text and Statements)"
    },
    {
      "id": "n8",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 7,
      "text": "• Read one longer text"
    },
    {
      "id": "n9",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 8,
      "text": "• Decide whether each statement is richtig (+) or falsch (-)"
    },
    {
      "id": "n10",
      "type": "heading",
      "order": 9,
      "level": 4,
      "text": "Teil 3: Anzeigen und Situationen (Advertisements and Situations)"
    },
    {
      "id": "n11",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 10,
      "text": "• Read several advertisements and short situations"
    },
    {
      "id": "n12",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 11,
      "text": "• Match the correct advertisement to each situation"
